logicalColumns.name: Linkage Rate
logicalColumns.description: Exchange rate from Linked currency to Original PO currency

logicalColumns.name: Rate To Usd
logicalColumns.description:
Exchange Rate from PO original currency (before linkage) 
to USD at PO Header Creation Date

logicalColumns.name: Rate To Functional Currency
logicalColumns.description:
Exchange Rate from PO original currency (before linkage) 
to operating unit functional currency  at PO Header Creation Date

logicalColumns.name: Rate to USD (BOY)
logicalColumns.description:
Exchange rate from the po_currency to USD at January 1st the year of "first approved date".
BOY = Beginning Of Year

physicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN  TRUNCATE(%1, 0) <=  VALUEOF(%2) THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END

logicalColumns.name: Approved PR to PO SLA (PO OU WD)

physicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 = 81 THEN %2 - %3 - 2 *  FLOOR((%2 - %3) / 7) +  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) < 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 7 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 6 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 6 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) ELSE -(2) END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %2) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) < 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) IN (6, 7) THEN -(2) - 1 + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE -(2) END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) IN (6, 7) THEN -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE 0 END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) > 0 AND  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 7 THEN -(2) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) > 0 AND  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 6 THEN -(1) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE 0 END  END  END  END  ELSE %2 - %3 - 2 *  FLOOR((%2 - %3) / 7) +  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) < 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 7 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 1 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %2) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) >= 0 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) ELSE -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 1 THEN -(1) - (%2 -  CAST (%2 AS DATE )) ELSE -(2) END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%2) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) IN (7, 1) THEN  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %2) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) >= 0 THEN -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE -(2) - 1 + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %2) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) < 0 THEN -(2) ELSE 0 END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %2) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) >= 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) <> 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK(%2) <> 7 THEN 0 ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK(%2) <> 7 THEN -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 7 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE -(1) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 END  END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK(%2) <> 7 THEN -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 7 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) <> 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK(%2) = 7 THEN -(1) +  CAST (%2 AS DATE ) + 1 - %2 ELSE 0 END  END  END  END  END  END  END
